content: There are certain groups of fans that want to worship their chosen artists whether Madonna, Beyonce, and Taylor Swift. There are also other groups of fans that just enjoy their favorite artists' music and performances e.g. fans of Diana Ross, Janet Jackson, Bon Jovi, etc
